subproject.description: The project seeks to build capacity and facilitate the process of taking climate change into account in all plans thus facilitating the country to cope with climate change and its adverse impacts, and to prepare the ground for Sierra Leone’s participation in CDM and other project based mechanisms that may emerge in the future.
